thread.title: Judy

author: Judy
title: Judy
text: So far everything has lived up to my expectations. Shipping is a little steep to get product in a timely fashion, especially for a first-time user. I have the Medi compression stockings, thigh high, with the beaded band. They are staying right where I want them. Anxiously awaiting the 'donner' as I think that will be a real plus in getting the stockings in place. Wish I had taken the plunge and ordered it with my initial order!
